getInitialPURL

public abstract ecologylab.net.ParsedURL getInitialPURL()
Description copied from interface: QandDownloadable
Get the ParsedURL that the Downloadable was initially created with. This could change due to server-side re-directs, or, as in ACM Portal, through semantic actions that substitute in the location slot the PDF's PURL for one that referred to a metadata page.
